### Payout Receipt API Endpoints

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Generate Receipt Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/generate-number
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 2. Create Payout Receipt (Payment Type - Settling Multiple Purchases)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109ca",
  "vendorId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109cb",
  "receiptDate": "2025-08-04T10:00:00.000Z",
  "paymentType": "Payment",
  "paymentRecords": [
    {
      "paymentMethod": "Bank Transfer",
      "paidFrom": "HDFC Current Account",
      "amountPaid": 45000,
      "tdsPercent": 2,
      "tdsDeductedAmount": 1000,
      "transactionCharge": 50,
      "referenceId": "TXN123456789",
      "notes": "Payment for multiple purchase orders"
    }
  ],
  "allocations": [
    {
      "purchaseId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109cc",
      "amount": 25000
    },
    {
      "purchaseId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109cd",
      "amount": 20000
    }
  ],
  "purpose": "Payment for goods received",
  "internalNotes": "Vendor has good payment history"
}

### 3. Create Advance Payment Receipt
POST {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109ca",
  "vendorId": "60d0fe4f5311236168a109cb",
  "receiptDate": "2025-08-04T10:00:00.000Z",
  "paymentType": "Advance",
  "paymentRecords": [
    {
      "paymentMethod": "UPI",
      "paidFrom": "Business UPI",
      "amountPaid": 15000,
      "tdsPercent": 0,
      "tdsDeductedAmount": 0,
      "transactionCharge": 0,
      "referenceId": "UPI789123456",
      "notes": "Advance payment for upcoming orders"
    }
  ],
  "allocations": [],
  "purpose": "Advance payment",
  "internalNotes": "For future orders"
}

### 4. Get All Payout Receipts with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts?page=1&limit=10&sortBy=receiptDate&sortOrder=desc&paymentType=Payment&dateFrom=2025-08-01&dateTo=2025-08-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Get Payout Receipt by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/60d0fe4f5311236168a109ce
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Update Payout Receipt
PUT {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/60d0fe4f5311236168a109ce
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "Updated payment purpose",
  "internalNotes": "Updated internal notes",
  "paymentRecords": [
    {
      "paymentMethod": "Bank Transfer",
      "paidFrom": "HDFC Current Account",
      "amountPaid": 45000,
      "tdsPercent": 2,
      "tdsDeductedAmount": 1000,
      "transactionCharge": 50,
      "referenceId": "TXN123456789",
      "notes": "Updated payment notes"
    }
  ]
}

### 7. Delete Payout Receipt
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/60d0fe4f5311236168a109ce
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Get Vendor's Pending Purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/vendor/60d0fe4f5311236168a109cb/pending-purchases
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Get Payout Receipt Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/stats?dateFrom=2025-08-01&dateTo=2025-08-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Get Payment Method Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts/payment-breakdown?dateFrom=2025-08-01&dateTo=2025-08-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 11. Search by Receipt Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts?receiptNumber=PAY-2025-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Filter by Vendor
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts?vendorId=60d0fe4f5311236168a109cb&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 13. Filter by Amount Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/payout-receipts?amountMin=10000&amountMax=50000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
